room_title: Escape room "The Cult of Mithras" by Dare To Escape AZ in Phoenix
room_description:
You are part of the Cult of Mithras. The cult has evolved into protectors of the Mithral stone over the centuries. It is centered around the William estate in England, owned by Cedric William IV, the grandmaster of the cult.
You are tasked with living near the estate and supporting William in case anything goes wrong. And one day it doesâ€¦ You each received a call from Isabella Prisca, the venerable historian of the cult. You must disable the defenses. Recover the stone and escape the room before the police arrive.
